{"tid":419864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老婆唔再比我食榴槤，尋晚炒左大鑊","createTime":"2017-10-01T00:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T04:35:45.000Z","uid":28938,"like":1760,"dislike":322,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"3640fcb0be28839c355d016538df8fe39b567d81","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:09:21.000Z","msg":"話說前日有個客送左幾個貓山王俾我，尋晚一路睇車鏝大戰一路食，老婆明明瞓左都走出黎話聞到好臭，我話依個係我飲食自由，講講下嘈起上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘈到咁上下見到迪布尼入世界波，心情更差，講左句「你個閪臭過榴連我都奶啦，八婆！」<br />\n<br />\n之後佢喊住咁返入房，今朝早粒聲唔出返左娘家，點算好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻去油麻地果欄買榴連，今日約埋知己一齊食榴連自助餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 氹返老婆，跪玻璃"},{"pid":"3f7c79118e87c6d4ffd5f69fa3d45d860dad0069","tid":419864,"uid":133611,"like":450,"dislike":6,"score":444,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"娶榴槤算啦你"},{"pid":"14e3c335a3f77b00a63400a9a0ba7d068a64fb18","tid":419864,"uid":86893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310fd4446f7279763041ea09bbb37f7b2f81b312","tid":419864,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:12:52.000Z","msg":"你收得皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734e547ea5f1d871009d969579937fb66a90254e","tid":419864,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243f8b84e83a8f9f659ab08c0f22a48162260faf","tid":419864,"uid":60651,"like":163,"dislike":2,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"塞舊榴槤落你老婆塊臭西度起勢咁奶，奶到起膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a50640f6bfca930bdfd271b8ec59ac35703a4","tid":419864,"uid":133611,"like":459,"dislike":29,"score":430,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:16:27.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n榴槤陣味真係唔係個個接受到<br />\n例如我<br />\n<br />\n我以前屋企人食榴槤嗰陣會喺廚房食<br />\n都唔會放過夜同放雪櫃<br />\n係尊重番唔鍾意呢陣味嘅成員<br />\n好似我有屋企人唔鍾意我陣香水味<br />\n咁我就唔喺屋企噴 等lift先噴<br />\n<br />\n你老婆聞到陣味好難頂<br />\n你要想辦法唔影響佢<br />\n<br />\n最後 你鬧番佢嗰句太過份<br />\n番娘家係咪太誇張就唔評論<br />\n因為唔知你平時點對佢<br />\n<br />\nsor for 認真mode"},{"pid":"310f257d143419e23e7399ff76ff7974fb5d5dd0","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":10,"dislike":22,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你收得皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經趁佢瞓左先食，就哂佢仲想點？"},{"pid":"8afb6f69d9dfc08c20f7285fe76347e969279586","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":37,"dislike":7,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>娶榴槤算啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣咁三尖八角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18f40f8e49263bca2edca8ecef232761c05fb1d","tid":419864,"uid":77318,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:28:24.000Z","msg":"同人地行一世就忍下啦"},{"pid":"8abbecdf1367c3a779735e2807d3f44db98edcd8","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塞舊榴槤落你老婆塊臭西度起勢咁奶，奶到起膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df94ea86bfd146b59715a4fd5268cf2cc001c1d6","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":19,"dislike":116,"score":-97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答<br />\n榴槤陣味真係唔係個個接受到<br />\n例如我<br />\n<br />\n我以前屋企人食榴槤嗰陣會喺廚房食<br />\n都唔會放過夜同放雪櫃<br />\n係尊重番唔鍾意呢陣味嘅成員<br />\n好似我有屋企人唔鍾意我陣香水味<br />\n咁我就唔喺屋企噴 等lift先噴<br />\n<br />\n你老婆聞到陣味好難頂<br />\n你要想辦法唔影響佢<br />\n<br />\n最後 你鬧番佢嗰句太過份<br />\n番娘家係咪太誇張就唔評論<br />\n因為唔知你平時點對佢<br />\n<br />\nsor for 認真mode</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大佬我已經趁佢瞓先敢食，已經完全尊重佢"},{"pid":"f9ab24b3d74bb0e6c75a003a5523b086f722f975","tid":419864,"uid":17623,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:40:47.000Z","msg":"Chong ho ball"},{"pid":"1047d19f0808b9d65383f5ba6d3041d4c900f799","tid":419864,"uid":46452,"like":121,"dislike":13,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"買啲比榴槤更臭既野帶埋去外母度。<br />\n同老婆講，你搵到隻比你個閪臭既野啦<br />\n其實你個閪都唔係好臭姐"},{"pid":"5c0b3b52227586e4d4d44d7dccf66976b34dbd70","tid":419864,"uid":28938,"like":619,"dislike":4,"score":615,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買啲比榴槤更臭既野帶埋去外母度。<br />\n同老婆講，你搵到隻比你個閪臭既野啦<br />\n其實你個閪都唔係好臭姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你把口邊度有得賣？"},{"pid":"ce64f1540e089e3ed805533ce6095fa862204c2b","tid":419864,"uid":10679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買啲比榴槤更臭既野帶埋去外母度。<br />\n同老婆講，你搵到隻比你個閪臭既野啦<br />\n其實你個閪都唔係好臭姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你把口邊度有得賣？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8004d1989971b235dd4c38c864c2203290cef71a","tid":419864,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買啲比榴槤更臭既野帶埋去外母度。<br />\n同老婆講，你搵到隻比你個閪臭既野啦<br />\n其實你個閪都唔係好臭姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你把口邊度有得賣？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5deb9c106654e4eb34a117ed8437ba5406fe53","tid":419864,"uid":29001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買啲比榴槤更臭既野帶埋去外母度。<br />\n同老婆講，你搵到隻比你個閪臭既野啦<br />\n其實你個閪都唔係好臭姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你把口邊度有得賣？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asset